      "description": "Offering a truly surgical example of precision engineering. This unit features a Stage 2 optimized ECU map paired with a high-flow induction system, ensuring a linear power band and peak torque delivery. The chassis has been stiffened with upgraded bushings to eliminate deflection, providing razor-sharp turn-in and zero-lash response. Maintenance has been obsessive, including 3,000-mile synthetic cycles and a recent cooling system refresh with a high-capacity aluminum core. Every seal is bone-dry, and the compression numbers are perfectly balanced across all cylinders. This is a factory-plus build for the driver who demands peak mechanical harmony.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
